e NO post 50 spells that go to waste.</b></P><P>There are always going to be useless spells but I agree that there should be far fewer post 50 that have little or no use.</P><P>Philiak Mortus Lv.51 Necromancer of Xev<BR>Zeratis Lv.30 Monkey<BR>Sam: Where should I put this thing so that it doesnt hurt anyone we know or care about?<BR>Max: Out the window Sam. There's nobody but strangers out there.<BR><a href="http://www.pvponline.com" target="_blank">www.pvponline.com</a></font></td>
